<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
	<!-- Standard Meta -->
	<meta charset="utf-8" />
	<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge,chrome=1" />
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0">

	<!-- Site Properities -->
	<title><%= title %></title>
	<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/libs/semantic/semantic.min.css">
	<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/styles.css">
	<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/about.css">
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Google Analytics -->
    <% include common/analytics %>

    <!-- Mobile Sidebar -->
    <% include common/sidebar %>

	<!-- Page Contents -->
	<div class="pusher">
		<% include common/nav %>

		<div class="ui vertical inverted stripe segment title">
			<div class="ui middle aligned stackable grid container">
				<div class="row">
					<div class="column">
						<h1><%= header %></h1>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="ui vertical stripe segment">
			<div class="ui middle aligned stackable grid container">
				<div class="row">
					<div class="ten wide column">
						<p><b>
							My name is Tom Fischer, and I am from Teeswater Ontario. I am entering my 4th year in Software Engineering at Western University. I am currently a Software Developer intern at IBM, where I work on new features in JavaScript/Dojo and Java.
						</b></p>
						<p>
							I have designed and developed various applications and websites over the years. Most of my projects are written using NodeJS, Java, or C#. Along with these skills, I also have experience with SQL and NoSQL databases.
						</p>
						<p>
							Besides programming, I enjoy playing sports, snowboarding, and snowmobiling. I have played hockey and baseball for most of my life, and I continue to play today. I also play recreational badminton and innertube water polo at Western University.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="six wide column">
						<img src="/images/tom-alt-min.JPG" class="ui rounded image">
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="ui vertical inverted stripe segment">
			<div class="ui middle aligned center aligned stackable grid container">
				<div class="row">
					<div class="column">
						<h1 class="ui inverted header">Social Networks</h1>
						<div class="ui inverted horizontal divider"><i class="desktop icon"></i></div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="three column row">
					<div class="column">
						<h1><i class="huge white github icon"></i></h1>
						<h2 class="header"><a href="https://github.com/tgfischer" class="white-link" target="_blank">Github Profile</a></h2>
					</div>
					<div class="column">
						<h1><i class="huge blue linkedin icon"></i></h1>
						<h2 class="header"><a href="https://ca.linkedin.com/in/tom-fischer-38179946" class="white-link" target="_blank">Linkedin Profile</a></h2>
					</div>
					<div class="column">
						<h1><i class="huge orange stack overflow icon"></i></h1>
						<h2 class="header"><a href="http://stackoverflow.com/users/2455765/tfischer" class="white-link" target="_blank">Stack Overflow Profile</a></h2>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<% include common/footer %>
	</div>

	<script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-1.11.3.min.js"></script>
	<script src="/libs/semantic/semantic.min.js"></script>
	<script src="/js/scripts.js"></script>

</body>

</html>
